{
 "name": "RPlog_Touchdown",
 "title": "Touchdown: Escape from the Nemesis",
 "summary": "The Jedi Leo Corak, flying a stolen TIE Avenger under the guise of the Sith 'Darth Venger,' threads the Imperial blockade above Caspar to cover the escape of the New Republic shuttle Ticonderoga. Aboard the shuttle, the marine pilot Amaya 'Halo' Halos fights to fly a damaged lambda crammed with freed prisoners, including the ailing Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard and the defecting Imperial medic Liora Kovani, while Delgard's young daughter Gabi seizes the comm to reach her mother. As the Nemesis declares a free-fire zone and TIE fighters give chase, Leo destroys the pursuers and transmits a hyperspace solution, and the Ticonderoga jumps clear just ahead of the turbolasers. Touching down at the New Republic base on New Alderaan, the survivors disembark; Gabi reunites with her mother, Kovani submits to processing, and Delgard's relief curdles into dread as she realizes the Empire had ransacked her child's room.",
